description: Early Works related to the New Champlain Bridge Corridor project including design, site preparation and mobilization.
comments: Early Work Agreement for the New Champlain Bridge Corridor project. This contract was awarded following a competitive process. However, no funds will be paid out of this contract, as in June 2015, the Project Agreement was signed (contract number 9202250101 dated June 19, 2015), cancelling this contract.
